<section autotoc="On this page">
    <title>
        SECTION 1: THINGS NEARBY &amp; IN YOUR INVENTORY
    </title>
    <section id="overview">
        <title>
            Overview
        </title>
        <p>
            Throughout your adventuring career you will discover, acquire, manipulate, and discard many items.
        </p>
        <p>
            Any tile on the main screen over which you can pass can hold one or more items. If the tile holds a pile of items only the topmost item is visible from any distance (and this can mean that, eg, a stone giant's throne is completely obscured by an arrow).
        </p>
    </section>
