                </p>
            </dd>
            <dt>
                <a href="./secn_1-3.dai">Section 1-3: Applying Things</a>
            </dt>
            <dd>
                <p>
                    To use an item, whether it be eating food or wearing a hat or wielding a weapon, you must apply it.
                </p>
            </dd>
            <dt>
                <a href="./secn_1-4.dai">Section 1-4: Containers</a>
            </dt>
            <dd>
                <p>
                    Certain items, such as bags and pouches, and bits of scenery, such as cupboards and shelves, are containers and may hold further items (which may themselves be containers) within.
                </p>
            </dd>
